BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Brightwood Speaks: Residents Against Metroblocks Data Center
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260401T093000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260401T113000
UID:f8c26816b493fc8b5889a34aea1712e9@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/Screenshot%202026-03-31%20175323_20260331215341474620.png
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we support LiveFree Indiana and the Black Church Co
 alition in preventing a data center from being built in a vulnerable commu
 nity against their will. This is an in-person meeting with the relevant co
 mmission where they will decide whether to build the data center. There ha
 s been a large community pushback against this initiative - help us push o
 ur resistance over the finish line!
LOCATION:200 E Washington St\, Indianapolis\, IN\, 46204
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblecentralindiana/event/931554/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Central Indiana (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
